WEBVTT

00:02.086 --> 00:03.044
So here's what's happened
on Glee.

00:03.128 --> 00:05.046
Finn got Kurt to try out
for the football team,

00:05.130 --> 00:07.757
but sometimes
it seems like maybe Kurt's
got a crush on him.

00:07.883 --> 00:10.259
It's enough to want to
give up women altogether.
[Chuckles]

00:10.344 --> 00:11.969
Will's old crush April
joined the Glee Club,

00:12.054 --> 00:14.138
but she was drunk all the time
so Will kicked her out.

00:14.223 --> 00:16.015
Also, Sue convinced
Kurt and Mercedes that they
should join the Cheerios,

00:16.100 --> 00:18.059
which Will was
none too happy about.

00:18.143 --> 00:19.936
And that's what you missed
on Glee.

00:21.772 --> 00:24.482
♪♪ [Marching Band Drums]

00:24.566 --> 00:27.944
Ladies, what we have here
is a grade-A dilemma.

00:28.028 --> 00:32.490
Mercedes, your vocal cords
have had more fantastic runs
than a Kenyan track team,

00:32.574 --> 00:35.159
but that look simply will not do.

00:35.244 --> 00:37.870
At first I thought
it was a subtle homage
to yours truly,

00:37.955 --> 00:40.289
but now I fear
it's some sort
of ironic comment.

00:40.374 --> 00:43.710
Ms. Sylvester,
I'm just not comfortable
in those Cheerios skirts.

00:43.794 --> 00:45.712
They don't fit me right.

00:45.796 --> 00:47.964
Mercedes, you shouldn't
feel embarrassed
about your body.

00:48.048 --> 00:49.674
