00:56.515 --> 00:58.641
How do you two
not have a show on Bravo?

00:59.768 --> 01:01.436
Here's the skinny.

01:01.520 --> 01:04.772
Splits magazine,
after much campaigning
by one Sue Sylvester,

01:04.857 --> 01:08.359
has named me
cheerleading coach
of the last 2,000 years.

01:08.444 --> 01:11.738
In seven days
reporter Tracy Pendergrass
will arrive on campus...

01:11.822 --> 01:14.741
and my new star singer
will have lost 10 pounds...

01:14.825 --> 01:17.243
and be in
a gender-appropriate
cheerleading uniform,

01:17.327 --> 01:19.662
or she is off the team.

01:22.082 --> 01:26.210
Ten pounds? Are you serious?
You could lose a few too, kiddo.
You got hips like a pear.

01:28.505 --> 01:31.799
Now, if you’ll excuse me,
I have to put in a call to
the Ohio secretary of state...

01:31.884 --> 01:35.011
notifying them
I will no longer
be carrying photo I.D.

01:35.095 --> 01:37.180
You know why?

01:37.264 --> 01:39.849
People should know
who I am.

01:43.020 --> 01:45.062
[School Bell Rings]
Sue! We need to talk.

01:45.147 --> 01:46.981
