is padlocked!

01:47.065 --> 01:49.734
Well, that's curious.
Did you check
the sign-up sheet?

01:49.818 --> 01:53.321
- What sign-up sheet?
- Why, the one I keep right here
in my waistband, William.

01:55.157 --> 01:58.409
Let's see. Yeah,
I've got the entire week
booked solid.

01:58.494 --> 02:01.078
Got a big magazine
feature coming up...

02:01.163 --> 02:03.706
